02-	LEI ESTADUA 16140 ART 139 CC ART 140; CC LEI COMPLEMENTAR 377/18 ART 33, I;
03-	DECRETI MUNICIPAL 8297 ART 55 CC ART 53;
04-	RDC 216/04 ITENS 4.2.1 CC 4.2.4;
05-	RDC 216/04 INTES 4.2.6;
